{"tid":1005720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梅西找上75歲老乾爹　周領5千還不用啪啪啪","createTime":"2019-02-02T12:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T12:37:02.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f724d6433657146b40bdd187cc86188505574788","tid":1005720,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:03:54.000Z","msg":"美國電視台《第五頻道》（Channel 5）近期推出節目「Banged Up: Bad Girls Behind Bars」，透露美國監獄的囚犯生活，其中一集專訪了因侵入民宅、綁架、毆打老婦人而遭逮捕的女囚梅西（Missy），而一名75歲的老鄰居卻對她不離不棄，不但在她入獄前就幫她扶養小孩達5年，在她入獄後更為她盡心盡力的付出。<br />\n對此，梅西也強調雖然「乾爹」每周都會給她150美元（約4,500元台幣）的零用錢，但2人也僅是以親吻表示愛意，從未發生過性關係，她認為這就像和親爺爺做愛一樣不是好事，同實也坦承未來出獄後能和「乾爹」結婚，這樣一來她就能每個月領4,000美元（約12萬元台幣）的養老金和社會補助金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20190202/1512391\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20190202%2F1512391&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2Y6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=e5d9c677\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20190202%2F1512391&h=af159f40\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20190202/1512391</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190202/640_e774cb46c673c7df0dd2e2b25852f624.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190202%2F640_e774cb46c673c7df0dd2e2b25852f624.jpg&h=8fab4ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190202/640_4e57e9488b8eac7c5247b07274b2ceed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190202%2F640_4e57e9488b8eac7c5247b07274b2ceed.jpg&h=e6eb7e95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a90e91a66bd46a04b24e282f4f51113c04b97f","tid":1005720,"uid":1767,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTim